d 'HLPDIR': module to find location(s) of help file
d
d hlpdir hlpname runs dir hlpname.hlp repeatedly for each directory
d or  folder along your adopath and gives a location for any copies
d  which it finds. This could be useful for (a) for finding a help
d file (b)  for keeping track of multiple versions of such a file.
d
